WEBVTT

00:08.880 --> 00:09.800
This northern expedition

00:10.240 --> 00:11.080
Our goal

00:11.400 --> 00:12.640
Is to retake Beiyu Pass

00:13.160 --> 00:14.800
To further expand the war

00:14.880 --> 00:16.360
And prepare to recover the realm

00:17.160 --> 00:18.280
If we can take this place

00:18.520 --> 00:18.840
Advancing

00:19.640 --> 00:20.960
We can follow the Hanshui upstream

00:21.480 --> 00:22.320
Straight to Guanzhong

00:23.640 --> 00:23.960
Retreating

00:24.480 --> 00:25.800
We can block the Luoshui

00:26.160 --> 00:27.000
To cut off enemy reinforcements

00:27.800 --> 00:29.840
Consolidate several key towns north of Tianhe

00:30.480 --> 00:31.080
In ten days

00:31.640 --> 00:32.840
I will lead the main force

00:33.040 --> 00:34.120
Cross the Tianhe and go north

00:34.400 --> 00:35.120
Enter Shuoyang

00:35.440 --> 00:36.320
First take Xingyang

00:36.720 --> 00:37.640
Then attack Beiyu Pass

00:38.600 --> 00:39.400
General Zheng Lu

00:39.400 --> 00:40.280
Zu Yue, receive orders

00:42.360 --> 00:42.920
Your general is here

00:44.360 --> 00:45.720
I order you to lead one army

00:46.040 --> 00:46.920
From Qigong Mountain

00:47.200 --> 00:48.400
Attack Chen and Qiao counties

00:48.760 --> 00:50.320
Sweep the surrounding Wutu tribes

00:50.640 --> 00:51.720
And northern rebels

00:52.280 --> 00:53.960
To pin down the Wutu Zhao main force

00:54.840 --> 00:55.520
Your general accepts the order

00:56.840 --> 00:58.040
General Pingbei Sikong Yao

01:01.640 --> 01:02.400
Your general is here

01:02.520 --> 01:03.920
I order you to lead one army

01:04.120 --> 01:05.200
From Ling Province northward

01:05.480 --> 01:06.560
Enter and garrison Yiyang City
